Ds differently from epics doc (10-2 vs 1.2 within Epic 1 of multi-framework epics). Old getDriver() stub references \"Epic 5\" — stale comment.\n\n## Token Report — create-story\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Read: 5, Glob: 5, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 10-1-agentdriver-interface-types — create-story (2026-04-03T06:20)\n\n- **Workaround: Epic numbering mismatch.** Sprint-status uses \"Epic 10\" (10-1, 10-2...) but epics file uses \"Epic 1\" internally (Story 1.1, 1.2...). Mapped 10-1 to Epic 1 Story 1.1 in the multi-framework epics.\n- **Risk: `OutputContract` type placement.** Architecture places `output-contract.ts` as a separate module, but the type needs to be in `types.ts` because `DispatchOpts` references it. TYPE in `types.ts`, IMPLEMENTATION in later story.\n- **Observation:** Existing `AgentDriver` interface is very different from target (process-based vs async-iterable-based). Deprecated type preservation important — 288 lines of tests against old interface.\n\n## Token Report — create-story\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 10, Glob: 6, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Files read: 12 unique, 12 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 10-1-agentdriver-interface-types — dev-story (2026-04-03T06:25)\n\nNo issues reported. Clean implementation — 4 files modified, 30+ tests, all 4219 tests passing.\n\n## Token Report — dev-story\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 5, Edit: 13, Grep: 3, Write: 3, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~40 lines), `npx tsc --noEmit` (~30 lines), `npm run build` (~15 lines)\n- Files read: 6 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none significant\n\n### 10-1-agentdriver-interface-types — code-review (2026-04-03T06:30)\n\n- **HIGH fixed:** `DispatchOpts` fields mutable — drivers could mutate caller's options. Added `readonly`.\n- **MEDIUM fixed (x4):** Mutable fields on `DriverHealth`, `DriverCapabilities`, `OutputContract`, `TestResults`, `ACStatus`.\n- **MEDIUM fixed:** Test name/count mismatch (\"8 event types\" vs 9 actual).\n- **MEDIUM fixed:** `ErrorCategory` exhaustiveness test was cosmetic, not compile-time safe. Added `never` switch.\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `ACStatus.status` is typed as `string` rather than a union type.\n- **LOW (not fixed):** `SpawnOpts` deprecated type still uses mutable fields (scheduled for removal in 10-3).\n- **Architecture concern:** Story AC #1 added `capabilities` to `AgentDriver` interface, which isn't in the architecture spec (Decision 1). Spec drift.\n- Coverage: 96.75% overall, all 163 files above 80%.\n\n## Token Report — code-review\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 7, Edit: 8, Grep: 2, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git diff` (~30 lines), `npm run build` (~18 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads\n- Redundant operations: `npm run build` ran twice (both necessary)\n\n### 10-1-agentdriver-interface-types — verification (2026-04-03T06:35)\n\n- 51 pre-existing lint warnings (unused vars) — unrelated to this story\n- `codeharness verify` warns about missing Showboat and exec-plan — non-blocking\n- ALL_PASS 11/11 ACs with real evidence\n\n## Token Report — verification\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 5, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:coverage` (~50 lines), `npm run test:unit` (~40 lines)\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: `npm run build` ran twice (minor)\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":109,"oldLines":6,"newStart":109,"newLines":19,"lines":[" - Files read: 5 unique, 6 total reads"," - Redundant operations: Coverage and test:unit run separately (could be one), verify run 3 times due to proof format fixes"," ","+### 10-2-driver-factory-registry — verification (2026-04-03T10:55)","+","+- `codeharness verify` exits code 1 due to AGENTS.md doc-gate (missing factory.ts) — harness precondition, not AC failure","+- BATS integration tests show code 127 warnings — pre-existing, unrelated","+- ALL_PASS 10/10 ACs with real evidence, factory.ts at 100% coverage","+","+## Token Report — verification","+- Total tool calls: 14","+- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 5, Grep: 1, Write: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test` (~80 lines), `npx vitest run --reporter=verbose` (~60 lines), `npm run test:coverage` (~40 lines)","+- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads","+- Redundant operations: overlapping `npm test` and `npx vitest run --reporter=verbose` calls","+"," ### 10-2-driver-factory-registry — code-review (2026-04-03T10:48)"," "," - **MEDIUM fixed:** `registerDriver(null)` crashes with unhelpful TypeError — added input validation"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
